<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18,147" end="00:00:22,407">Ett, tv&#229;. Ett, tv&#229;, tre, fyr</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22,537" end="00:00:23,457"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23,582" end="00:00:25,691">Om du tycker om James Browns musik </p>
      <p begin="00:00:25,691" end="00:00:27,585">kommer du ha riktigt roligt ikv&#228;ll.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27,585" end="00:00:29,761">Ikv&#228;ll firar vi Black Velvet,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29,761" end="00:00:33,850">James Brown Jr.'s 62:a f&#246;delsedag</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33,852" end="00:00:36,442" region="top"> Whoo, 62!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:36,472" end="00:00:38,502" region="top"> S&#229; ge en varm appl&#229;d</p>
      <p begin="00:00:38,526" end="00:00:39,758" region="top"> till den h&#228;r unge mannen</p>
      <p begin="00:00:39,758" end="00:00:41,545" region="top"> som &#228;r p&#229; v&#228;g upp p&#229; scenen</p>
      <p begin="00:00:41,545" end="00:00:43,690">Han har varit p&#229; David Letterman Show,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43,690" end="00:00:45,777">H&#228;lsa honom v&#228;lkommen med en stor appl&#229;d</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45,777" end="00:00:49,963">Black Velvet, James Brown, Jr!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49,963" end="00:00:52,279"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52,279" end="00:00:53,952"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53,952" end="00:00:59,249">&#9834; Det &#228;r en mans v&#228;rld. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59,249" end="00:01:05,556">&#9834; Men den &#228;r inget, inget... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05,556" end="00:01:06,715">- Jag har spelat James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06,715" end="00:01:13,956">sen jag var 14 &#229;r gammal.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13,956" end="00:01:16,475"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16,475" end="00:01:17,935"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17,945" end="00:01:21,265"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21,265" end="00:01:25,855"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25,855" end="00:01:29,767">Men nu vill jag vara Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29,767" end="00:01:52,445"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52,599" end="00:01:54,471" region="top"> Min f&#246;rsta skiva med egna l&#229;tar</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54,471" end="00:01:58,132" region="top"> sl&#228;pps den 25:e januari.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58,132" end="00:02:01,271">Jag har k&#228;mpat i &#246;ver 42 &#229;r</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01,271" end="00:02:03,014">f&#246;r att lyckas i branschen</p>
      <p begin="00:02:03,014" end="00:02:04,731">och vid 62 &#229;rs &#229;lder</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04,731" end="00:02:06,775">b&#246;rjar jag &#228;ntligen se en ljusning.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09,086" end="00:02:11,071">Jag har aldrig tj&#228;nat nog med pengar</p>
      <p begin="00:02:11,071" end="00:02:13,928">f&#246;r att f&#246;rs&#246;rja mig p&#229; musiken,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13,928" end="00:02:15,993">men jag hoppas att den h&#228;r skivan</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15,993" end="00:02:17,442">ska bli en v&#228;ndpunkt</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17,442" end="00:02:20,252">s&#229; att jag kan f&#246;rs&#246;rja mig p&#229; musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25,314" end="00:02:26,837">Du....</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26,837" end="00:02:28,808">Jag h&#228;mtar lite vatten &#229;t dig, OK?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28,808" end="00:02:30,155">H&#246;rru.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30,155" end="00:02:31,134">Det d&#228;r &#228;r min f&#229;gel.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:31,134" end="00:02:32,647">Den g&#246;r mig arg.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32,647" end="00:02:33,782">N&#228;r jag blir arg g&#229;r jag d&#228;rifr&#229;n</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33,782" end="00:02:35,520">till ett annat rum och st&#228;nger d&#246;rren,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35,520" end="00:02:37,328">l&#229;ter honom skrika s&#229; mycket han vill.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38,020" end="00:02:39,057">Jag har mitt eget lilla st&#228;lle.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:39,057" end="00:02:40,590">Det &#228;r inte precis vad jag vill ha</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40,590" end="00:02:43,199">men jag tackar Gud att jag har en bostad.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44,221" end="00:02:45,529">N&#228;r jag g&#229;r in i min lilla l&#228;genhet</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45,529" end="00:02:47,113">och l&#229;ser d&#246;rren</p>
      <p begin="00:02:47,113" end="00:02:48,734">k&#228;nner jag mig tillfreds.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48,734" end="00:02:50,496">Men n&#228;r jag &#229;ker till ghettot,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50,496" end="00:02:53,225">g&#229;r in i hissen,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53,225" end="00:02:54,407">kommer dit,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54,407" end="00:02:55,545">det &#228;r d&#229; problemen b&#246;rjar.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55,545" end="00:02:57,076">Man vet aldrig</p>
      <p begin="00:02:57,076" end="00:02:59,174">vad som kan h&#228;nda d&#228;r inne.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:59,174" end="00:03:00,663">Vi kom ner</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00,663" end="00:03:02,366">och s&#229;g Alfred.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02,366" end="00:03:03,206">Bra kille, st&#246;rde aldrig n&#229;gon.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03,206" end="00:03:04,783">En kyrkokille.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04,783" end="00:03:06,731">De har skjutit in i hans l&#228;genhet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06,731" end="00:03:08,463">Han visade mig var de hade skjutit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08,478" end="00:03:10,701">Jag sa: "Wow, man." Jag sa:</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10,741" end="00:03:13,017">"Jag vill inte bo p&#229; bottenv&#229;ningen."</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13,017" end="00:03:14,586">- N&#228;r det blir f&#246;r galet</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14,586" end="00:03:16,289">i ghettot</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16,289" end="00:03:18,007">&#229;ker jag till min mammas hus</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18,007" end="00:03:19,737">och sover i hennes k&#228;llare.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32,075" end="00:03:33,691">- S&#229; jag kommer hit</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33,691" end="00:03:36,011">och det &#228;r h&#228;r jag sover.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:36,011" end="00:03:37,269">Tills n&#228;sta dag</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37,269" end="00:03:39,058">d&#229; jag tar hand om deras &#228;renden.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39,058" end="00:03:40,105">Tar hand om allt som beh&#246;vs</p>
      <p begin="00:03:40,105" end="00:03:43,638">f&#246;r att ha vi ska ha tak &#246;ver huvudet.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43,931" end="00:03:47,370">- Jag tycker om att rulla ihop det h&#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47,370" end="00:03:48,964">till en liten boll.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50,953" end="00:03:53,302">- Sl&#228;ng i dem h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55,722" end="00:03:56,898">- Hur g&#229;r det med riset?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:57,067" end="00:03:58,366">- L&#229;t mig se?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:00,135" end="00:04:02,056">En liten stund till.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:02,194" end="00:04:05,126">- Vi var 8 personer i v&#229;r familj.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:05,188" end="00:04:08,021">Mitt huvudm&#229;l var att ta hand om</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08,021" end="00:04:11,799">min mamma s&#229; bra som m&#246;jligt.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12,707" end="00:04:14,664" region="top"> - Han &#228;r min gullunge</p>
      <p begin="00:04:14,664" end="00:04:16,777" region="top"> och jag &#228;lskar honom.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16,883" end="00:04:18,556" region="top"> Han tv&#228;ttar mina kl&#228;der.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:18,726" end="00:04:19,466" region="top"> Han st&#228;dar mitt hus.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19,466" end="00:04:20,945" region="top"> P&#229; Alla hj&#228;rtans dag</p>
      <p begin="00:04:20,945" end="00:04:23,555" region="top"> kom han med en l&#229;da godis.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:23,555" end="00:04:24,911" region="top"> Han &#228;r lika s&#246;t</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24,911" end="00:04:26,138" region="top"> som godisl&#229;dan.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:26,138" end="00:04:27,835">- Jag vill bara</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27,835" end="00:04:28,542">att hennes liv ska vara fridfullt</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28,542" end="00:04:29,668">s&#229; att</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29,668" end="00:04:31,712">hon slipper oroa sig f&#246;r r&#228;kningar</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31,712" end="00:04:33,312">och s&#229;nt.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33,312" end="00:04:34,478">- Jag tog p&#229; mig det ansvaret</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34,478" end="00:04:36,190">men jag visste inte riktigt</p>
      <p begin="00:04:36,190" end="00:04:37,731">vad jag hade gett mig in p&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37,731" end="00:04:38,693">Men nu har jag redan b&#246;rjat.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38,693" end="00:04:40,083">Jag kommer inte att &#228;ndra mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40,083" end="00:04:41,252">S&#229; det enda jag kan g&#246;ra &#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:04:41,252" end="00:04:42,968">att f&#246;rs&#246;ka hitta ett s&#228;tt att f&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42,968" end="00:04:44,297">en stadig inkomst</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44,297" end="00:04:47,211">s&#229; jag kan klara mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:47,211" end="00:04:50,030">Mer &#228;n s&#229; kan jag inte beg&#228;ra just nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56,875" end="00:05:00,615">&#9834; Runt och runt &#229;ker vi igen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00,615" end="00:05:05,222">&#9834; Vart tar det v&#228;gen, ingen vet.. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:05,222" end="00:05:08,565">&#9834; Det &#228;r en kall kall v&#228;rld.&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08,965" end="00:05:12,469">&#9834; Det &#228;r en kall kall v&#228;rld. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14,254" end="00:05:16,173">&#9834; Hur kan vi stoppa f&#246;r&#228;ndringarna &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16,173" end="00:05:21,219">&#9834; som sker i USA idag?&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:31,033" end="00:05:35,022">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41,466" end="00:05:43,575">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaks. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43,575" end="00:05:47,287">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaks till gyllene tiderna. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:47,287" end="00:05:48,994">&#9834; Oh. Ah. Uh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49,455" end="00:05:50,963">&#9834; Ta mig tillbaka. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50,963" end="00:05:55,504">&#9834; Tillbaka till de gyllene tiderna. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55,504" end="00:05:58,215">&#9834; Rasera allt. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58,215" end="00:06:11,544"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11,564" end="00:06:13,438">- Det var en s&#229;ng</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13,438" end="00:06:15,399">fr&#229;n nya skivan "No Time For Dreaming."</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15,399" end="00:06:16,525">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16,525" end="00:06:17,652">and the Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17,652" end="00:06:19,111">- Jag kan inte fatta</p>
      <p begin="00:06:19,111" end="00:06:20,445">att du kom fr&#229;n ingenstans</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20,445" end="00:06:22,656">helt ok&#228;nd f&#246;r oss.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22,656" end="00:06:24,858">- Har du spelat in f&#246;rut?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24,981" end="00:06:26,277">- Nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:26,277" end="00:06:28,820">Det &#228;r min f&#246;rsta inspelning, som sl&#228;pps.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28,820" end="00:06:30,349">- Jag vet att du har upptr&#228;tt f&#246;rut.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30,349" end="00:06:31,431">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31,431" end="00:06:32,420">- Som Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32,420" end="00:06:34,044">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34,044" end="00:06:35,335">- S&#229; nu upptr&#228;der du som</p>
      <p begin="00:06:35,335" end="00:06:37,064">som Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37,064" end="00:06:38,076">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38,076" end="00:06:39,298">- Du har ett riktigt bra band</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39,298" end="00:06:40,129">bakom dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:40,129" end="00:06:41,667">Och sj&#228;lvklart</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41,667" end="00:06:43,302">de som jobbar p&#229; Daptone</p>
      <p begin="00:06:43,302" end="00:06:44,463">jag menar</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44,463" end="00:06:45,287">vilken fantastisk grupp de &#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:45,287" end="00:06:46,597">- Och du har sett vad som</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46,597" end="00:06:49,276">h&#228;nde med Sharon Jones, som...<br/>- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49,276" end="00:06:51,340">som, precis som du</p>
      <p begin="00:06:51,340" end="00:06:52,882">gick fr&#229;n totalt ok&#228;nd till</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52,897" end="00:06:55,464">vem vet hur h&#246;gt du kan n&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55,464" end="00:06:56,872">- Det &#228;r v&#228;l</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56,872" end="00:06:59,067">en sp&#228;nnande tid f&#246;r dig?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:59,067" end="00:07:01,820">- Jag tror Gud har besvarat mina b&#246;ner</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01,820" end="00:07:03,864">vet du, jag har</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03,864" end="00:07:06,033">fr&#229;gat mig sj&#228;lv varf&#246;r det dr&#246;jde</p>
      <p begin="00:07:06,033" end="00:07:07,451">men du kan inte ifr&#229;gas&#228;tta Gud</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07,451" end="00:07:09,411">n&#228;r han vill g&#246;ra n&#229;gonting.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:09,411" end="00:07:12,348">S&#229; i min &#229;lder b&#246;rjade det h&#228;nda saker.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:12,348" end="00:07:13,916">- Vad &#228;r n&#228;sta steg?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13,916" end="00:07:15,375">Jag menar, har du stora planer?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15,375" end="00:07:17,144">- Jag t&#228;nker att himlen &#228;r gr&#228;nsen.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:17,144" end="00:07:19,421">- Gratulerar till en fantastisk skiva.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:19,421" end="00:07:20,737">Oavsett vad som h&#228;nder med den</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20,737" end="00:07:22,632">&#228;r den ett riktigt konstverk.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22,632" end="00:07:24,943">Charles Bradley p&#229; WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:25,113" end="00:07:28,346"/>
      <p begin="00:07:28,346" end="00:07:33,685">&#9834; V&#228;rlden st&#229;r i brand. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33,685" end="00:07:39,107">&#9834; Ingen vill ta p&#229; sig ansvaret. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:39,107" end="00:07:44,286">&#9834; S&#228;g inte hur jag ska leva mitt liv. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:44,286" end="00:07:49,746">&#9834; N&#228;r du aldrig k&#228;nt sm&#228;rtan. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49,746" end="00:07:55,790">&#9834; Ohh. Ahh. Ohh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55,790" end="00:07:58,335">&#9834; Ohh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58,335" end="00:08:01,051">&#9834; Ser de inte att jag gr&#229;ter? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:01,051" end="00:08:02,883" region="top"> &#9834; Ohhh... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:02,883" end="00:08:04,800"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04,800" end="00:08:06,051" region="top"> - Jag vet inte hur m&#229;nga artister</p>
      <p begin="00:08:06,051" end="00:08:07,718" region="top"> som varit 62 &#229;r gamla</p>
      <p begin="00:08:07,718" end="00:08:09,445" region="top"> n&#228;r de sl&#228;ppte sin debutskiva.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:10,213" end="00:08:11,950" region="top"> Han kan vara den f&#246;rsta.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12,777" end="00:08:14,936" region="top"> - Han har bara b&#246;rjat</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14,936" end="00:08:16,937" region="top"> komma ig&#229;ng, s&#229; vitt jag kan se.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:16,937" end="00:08:19,215" region="top"> Han har jobbat h&#229;rt under l&#229;ng tid.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:19,338" end="00:08:20,858" region="top"> Och jag hoppas att</p>
      <p begin="00:08:20,858" end="00:08:21,734" region="top"> tillr&#228;ckligt m&#229;nga <br/>kan h&#246;ra honom sjunga</p>
      <p begin="00:08:21,734" end="00:08:23,151">s&#229; han kan</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23,151" end="00:08:24,361">f&#229; det liv han vill ha</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24,361" end="00:08:26,139">och kunna ta hand om sin familj.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:27,626" end="00:08:30,701">&#9834; Uh. Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30,701" end="00:08:33,120">&#9834; Jag pratar med dig tjejen. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:33,120" end="00:08:34,538">&#9834; Yeah. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34,538" end="00:08:36,642">&#9834; Bara dig... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36,642" end="00:08:38,333">- Jag gick till Gabe,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:38,333" end="00:08:40,502">jag t&#228;nkte att han vet vad han g&#246;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40,502" end="00:08:42,129">Jag k&#228;nde att han kunde hj&#228;lpa mig</p>
      <p begin="00:08:42,129" end="00:08:44,673">att ta mig in i musikbranschen.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44,673" end="00:08:48,569">Jag vet bara hur man upptr&#228;der p&#229; scen.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48,692" end="00:08:52,118">- Gillar du funk n' soul eller Afrobeat</p>
      <p begin="00:08:52,226" end="00:08:55,036">&#228;r det Gabe Roth du vill ska producera.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:55,174" end="00:08:57,708">Han kommer att leda dig i r&#228;tt</p>
      <p begin="00:08:57,708" end="00:08:59,778">eftersom deras skivor &#228;r fenomenala.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:00,994" end="00:09:03,773">- Jag b&#246;rjade g&#246;ra skivor som jag gillar.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:03,849" end="00:09:05,318">M&#229;nga soulskivor har en viss</p>
      <p begin="00:09:05,318" end="00:09:09,204">&#228;rlighet som jag gillar.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:11,137" end="00:09:12,724">En morgon, jag tror det var ganska tidigt,</p>
      <p begin="00:09:12,832" end="00:09:14,266">kanske runt 9 eller 10 p&#229; morgonen,</p>
      <p begin="00:09:14,297" end="00:09:16,394">knackade det p&#229; d&#246;rren<br/>och d&#228;r stod Charles.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:16,532" end="00:09:18,932">Han sa: "H&#246;rde att du letar efter s&#229;ngare"</p>
      <p begin="00:09:19,040" end="00:09:20,668">"Jag h&#246;rde att du letade efter mig."</p>
      <p begin="00:09:21,268" end="00:09:23,092">Jag f&#246;rstod inte vad han pratade om.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:23,092" end="00:09:25,506">S&#229; han visade mig ett videoklipp.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:25,506" end="00:09:26,784">Och han sjunger s&#229; bra, du vet?</p>
      <p begin="00:09:27,538" end="00:09:30,920">- Gabe Roth tog med honom till ett rep</p>
      <p begin="00:09:30,920" end="00:09:32,412">i Staten Island.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:32,412" end="00:09:34,470">Och Gabe ville spela in med en s&#229;ngare.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:34,500" end="00:09:36,613">Charles var en s&#229;ngare som</p>
      <p begin="00:09:36,613" end="00:09:38,004">Daptone inte hade hittat ett band till &#228;n</p>
      <p begin="00:09:38,004" end="00:09:40,048">men Charles f&#229;ngade deras uppm&#228;rksamhet.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:40,140" end="00:09:43,803">- Vi ser hur de fungerar tillsammans?</p>
      <p begin="00:09:43,926" end="00:09:47,401" region="top"> &#9834; Sluta &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:47,401" end="00:09:51,782" region="top"> &#9834; Sluta baby. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:51,782" end="00:09:55,952">&#9834; Ohhh. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:55,952" end="00:09:59,665">&#9834; Jag m&#229;r d&#229;ligt, baby. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:09:59,665" end="00:10:01,958">&#9834; Och jag &#228;r inl&#229;st i en bur...&#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01,958" end="00:10:06,661">- Jag spelade med Tommys band.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:07,110" end="00:10:09,636">Jag gick &#246;ver en dag n&#228;r de repade.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:09,636" end="00:10:11,635">De jammade och fr&#229;gade mig:</p>
      <p begin="00:10:11,635" end="00:10:14,930">"Kan du sjunga till detta?"</p>
      <p begin="00:10:14,930" end="00:10:18,684">Och du vet, jag gillade musiken,</p>
      <p begin="00:10:18,684" end="00:10:20,269">och texten bara kom till mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:20,269" end="00:10:24,188">- Det l&#246;ste sig bra. Vi spelade in l&#229;tarna</p>
