      <p begin="00:11:55,580" end="00:11:59,835">S&#229; n&#228;r vi repar och n&#228;r vi st&#229;r p&#229; scen,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:59,835" end="00:12:00,917">&#228;r tv&#229; helt olika saker.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:00,917" end="00:12:03,957">Bandet m&#229;ste vara samspelt, <br/>det enda vi f&#246;rs&#246;ker repa</p>
      <p begin="00:12:04,065" end="00:12:06,658">med Charles &#228;r att l&#229;ta honom leda.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:10,494" end="00:12:13,048">Bam, bam, bam, bam.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:14,771" end="00:12:16,723">- Tre, fyr.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:35,570" end="00:12:41,034">&#9834; I dig hittade jag k&#228;rleken. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:12:41,034" end="00:12:45,455">&#9834; Det f&#229;r mig att k&#228;nna mig levande. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:12:45,455" end="00:12:48,041">&#9834; Oh baby. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:12:48,041" end="00:12:55,461">&#9834; Ibland n&#228;r jag sover p&#229; kv&#228;llarna &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:12:55,461" end="00:13:02,973">&#9834; Vaknar jag och du &#228;r inte d&#228;r &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:13:02,973" end="00:13:10,773">&#9834; Du sa att du &#228;lskade mig, <br/>att du alltid skulle finnas d&#228;r. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:13:10,773" end="00:13:14,985">&#9834; I dig.. trodde jag att... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:13:14,985" end="00:13:18,032">- Den nya musiken &#228;r jag, <br/>f&#246;r en g&#229;ngs skull.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:18,032" end="00:13:21,492">Det &#228;r saker jag har g&#229;tt igenom,</p>
      <p begin="00:13:21,492" end="00:13:24,036">hj&#228;rtesorger och sm&#228;rtor.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:24,036" end="00:13:27,956">&#9834; Jag vill inte vara en d&#229;re mer &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:13:27,956" end="00:13:34,087"/>
      <p begin="00:13:34,087" end="00:13:37,953">Ja du, Bradley.<br/>Du v&#228;ntade tv&#229; g&#229;nger p&#229; trumpeterna.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:37,953" end="00:13:39,426">- Ja, det var perfekt.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:39,426" end="00:13:42,469"/>
      <p begin="00:13:42,469" end="00:13:43,981">- Jag skulle vilja s&#228;ga godnatt.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:43,981" end="00:13:46,321">Vi kan alltid g&#246;ra det igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:46,429" end="00:13:49,025">Det var en riktig fest, Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:49,178" end="00:13:50,726">- Javisst och..</p>
      <p begin="00:13:50,834" end="00:13:52,033">- det d&#228;r var perfekt.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:52,141" end="00:13:53,227">- Tack igen Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:53,227" end="00:13:54,460">Du vet att jag &#228;lskar dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:54,460" end="00:13:55,595">Tack min bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:55,749" end="00:13:57,570">Hejd&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:13:58,108" end="00:14:01,942">Jag har inte st&#228;ngt d&#246;rren.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:07,225" end="00:14:13,295"/>
      <p begin="00:14:13,295" end="00:14:14,525">- 9 &#189;.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:14,525" end="00:14:15,793">- Kom igen nu mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:15,793" end="00:14:18,200">F&#246;rst sa du sa 9, sen 8, och 8 &#189; .</p>
      <p begin="00:14:18,200" end="00:14:19,813">Jag skaffade 8.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:19,813" end="00:14:21,862">Nu vill du ha 9, eller 9 &#189;.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:21,862" end="00:14:24,168">Vad &#228;r det f&#246;r fel med skorna du har h&#228;r?</p>
      <p begin="00:14:26,889" end="00:14:28,459">- Mamma, du g&#246;r mig galen.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:30,185" end="00:14:32,030"/>
      <p begin="00:14:33,461" end="00:14:35,513">Herrregud,</p>
      <p begin="00:14:35,559" end="00:14:38,197">Det &#228;r jobbigt ibland.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:38,197" end="00:14:41,446">Det &#228;r sv&#229;rt f&#246;r jag kan, liksom,</p>
      <p begin="00:14:41,446" end="00:14:43,490">allt h&#228;nger p&#229; mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:43,490" end="00:14:45,965">Men om jag satte henne p&#229; ett hem, <br/>s&#229; skulle hon s&#228;kert d&#246;.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:45,965" end="00:14:47,096">Och det vet jag.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:47,818" end="00:14:49,808" region="top"> Jag fick en stroke f&#246;rut.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:50,422" end="00:14:52,874" region="top"> Jag har haft m&#229;nga hj&#228;rtattacker.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:52,936" end="00:14:54,246" region="top"> Ha en bra dag.</p>
      <p begin="00:14:54,246" end="00:14:57,836" region="top"> Men hj&#228;rtattacken<br/>kom n&#228;r min styvpappa dog,</p>
      <p begin="00:14:57,836" end="00:15:06,382" region="top"> n&#228;r min mormor dog och n&#228;r min man...</p>
      <p begin="00:15:06,382" end="00:15:07,767" region="top"> dog.</p>
      <p begin="00:15:10,044" end="00:15:14,153">- Hon sa: "L&#229;t mig tillbringa<br/>mina sista dagar i huset."</p>
      <p begin="00:15:14,492" end="00:15:16,924">Jag sa: "OK, mamma. Jag ordnar det."</p>
      <p begin="00:15:17,140" end="00:15:20,809">Men hon vet inte att jag inte har ett liv.</p>
      <p begin="00:15:21,409" end="00:15:23,186">Hon &#228;r mitt liv.</p>
      <p begin="00:15:23,570" end="00:15:29,102">Att vara tillsammans med n&#229;gon, <br/>jag vet inte hur man g&#246;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:15:29,348" end="00:16:13,946"/>
      <p begin="00:16:13,946" end="00:16:18,454" region="top"> - N&#228;r Charles mamma l&#228;mnade Florida<br/>f&#246;r att &#229;ka till New York,</p>
      <p begin="00:16:18,562" end="00:16:23,926" region="top"> var Charles bara 8 m&#229;nader gammal.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:25,295" end="00:16:30,925">Hon var borta s&#229; l&#228;nge att,<br/>n&#228;r hon kom tillbaks f&#246;rsta g&#229;ngen</p>
      <p begin="00:16:30,925" end="00:16:33,262">k&#228;nde han inte igen henne,<br/>han visste inte att hon var hans mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:34,122" end="00:16:37,105">Han trodde hans mormor var hans mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:38,843" end="00:16:41,408" region="top"> - Jag &#229;kte till New York f&#246;r att <br/>det skulle bli b&#228;ttre f&#246;r oss alla.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:42,654" end="00:16:46,609" region="top"> Jag och min make separerade,<br/>jag ville b&#228;ttra mig och jag lyckades.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:46,609" end="00:16:50,246" region="top"> Jag k&#246;pte huset p&#229; 843 Willoughby Ave.</p>
      <p begin="00:16:50,338" end="00:16:52,195">Mmm-hm</p>
      <p begin="00:16:52,410" end="00:17:02,065">- Hon &#246;vergav, kan man s&#228;ga,<br/>barnen f&#246;r att f&#246;lja efter.. en man</p>
      <p begin="00:17:03,279" end="00:17:06,688">som redan hade en fru,<br/>men som hon var galen i.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:08,379" end="00:17:10,802">Annars hade hon f&#246;rmodligen inte <br/>&#229;kt till New York.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:10,940" end="00:17:15,445">Jag var v&#228;l ungef&#228;r 7 eller 8 &#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:15,445" end="00:17:18,140">N&#228;r mamma kom, ber&#228;ttade hon f&#246;r mormor</p>
      <p begin="00:17:18,217" end="00:17:20,106">att hon ville att jag skulle<br/>f&#246;lja med henne tillbaka.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:20,106" end="00:17:23,104">Min mormor sa: "Nej, l&#229;t dem stanna h&#228;r,<br/>de har det b&#228;ttre h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:23,196" end="00:17:26,138">"De kommer f&#229; en b&#228;ttre utbildning<br/>om de stannar h&#228;r med mig."</p>
      <p begin="00:17:26,368" end="00:17:28,062">Min mamma sa nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:28,200" end="00:17:30,392">S&#229; min mormor sa:<br/>"Nej, jag l&#229;ter dig inte ta dem."</p>
      <p begin="00:17:30,485" end="00:17:32,168">S&#229; min mamma stal oss.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:32,276" end="00:17:34,196" region="top"> - De var mina, s&#229; jag t&#228;nkte:</p>
      <p begin="00:17:34,196" end="00:17:36,881" region="top"> "Jag tar dem. Jag skapade dem."</p>
      <p begin="00:17:37,034" end="00:17:40,983" region="top"> S&#229; jag tog med mig mina skapelser <br/>tillbaka till New York.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:40,983" end="00:17:43,479">Mmm-hm.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:44,252" end="00:17:45,801">Det gjorde jag.</p>
      <p begin="00:17:47,340" end="00:17:50,821">- Jag hatar verkligen att s&#228;ga det</p>
      <p begin="00:17:50,821" end="00:17:51,998">men ibland var det sv&#229;rt<br/>att hitta n&#229;gra jobb</p>
      <p begin="00:17:51,998" end="00:17:56,906" region="top"> s&#229; det fanns bara en v&#228;g,<br/>om du hade n&#229;gon typ av anh&#246;riga</p>
      <p begin="00:17:57,690" end="00:18:00,561">s&#229; kunde du f&#229; lite bidrag.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:00,946" end="00:18:06,534">Och jag k&#228;nner att det var d&#228;rf&#246;r<br/>hon tog barnen, f&#246;r att f&#229; bidrag.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:07,179" end="00:18:11,262">- Under barndomen var han favoritbarnet.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:11,453" end="00:18:16,663">Han fick all k&#228;rlek och blev omh&#228;ndertagen<br/>av sina &#228;ldre br&#246;der,</p>
      <p begin="00:18:16,785" end="00:18:19,357">systrar, mormor och morbr&#246;der</p>
      <p begin="00:18:19,357" end="00:18:21,371">f&#246;r han var det lilla barnet.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:21,371" end="00:18:25,880">- N&#228;r Charles &#229;kte till New York,<br/>det var d&#229; han f&#246;rlorade allt det.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:31,834" end="00:18:32,928">- Jag bodde med min mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:32,928" end="00:18:36,312">Jag var r&#228;dd att hon skulle skada mig,<br/>s&#229; jag stack.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:36,312" end="00:18:38,457">Vi kom inte &#246;verens.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:38,457" end="00:18:39,997">Jag blev beskylld f&#246;r allt.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:39,997" end="00:18:41,508">S&#229; jag var v&#228;ldigt bitter.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:42,170" end="00:18:45,432">Det k&#228;ndes som att allt var ransonerat</p>
      <p begin="00:18:45,555" end="00:18:48,251">och jag bodde i en k&#228;llare<br/>som var v&#228;rre &#228;n den h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:48,251" end="00:18:52,166">Det var bara en sandk&#228;llare,<br/>inte en betongk&#228;llare.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:52,490" end="00:18:54,088">15 watts gl&#246;dlampa.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:54,195" end="00:18:55,982">Och jag k&#228;nde att:<br/>"Nej, jag klarar inte av det h&#228;r."</p>
      <p begin="00:18:56,012" end="00:18:57,752">Jag sa: "Jag vill inte mer, jag sticker."</p>
      <p begin="00:18:57,922" end="00:18:59,008">S&#229; jag stack.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:59,746" end="00:19:04,900"/>
      <p begin="00:19:04,900" end="00:19:07,056">Jag var 14 &#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:08,226" end="00:19:09,892">Tunnelbanan blev mitt hem.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:09,984" end="00:19:12,574">Jag gick dit f&#246;r att h&#229;lla mig varm.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:13,866" end="00:19:17,866">Jag satte mig p&#229; t&#229;get<br/>vissa kalla vintern&#228;tter.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:18,236" end="00:19:20,330">&#197;kte med t&#229;get fram och tillbaka.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:20,468" end="00:19:22,670">Polisen knackade h&#229;rt och sa:</p>
      <p begin="00:19:22,808" end="00:19:24,387">"Ungar, ni m&#229;ste g&#229; av."</p>
      <p begin="00:19:24,925" end="00:19:31,271">Jag gick &#246;ver till andra sidan perrongen,<br/>tog ett annat t&#229;g. Somnade igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:31,471" end="00:19:35,284">Satte mig i ett h&#246;rn,<br/>tog en pinne och slog h&#229;rt p&#229; n&#229;got.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:35,422" end="00:19:36,546">Det d&#228;r satte sig i mitt huvud.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:36,746" end="00:19:39,910">Han sa: "Upp med er ungar. Upp!"</p>
      <p begin="00:19:40,079" end="00:19:47,370">S&#229; jag &#229;kte olika turer<br/>f&#246;r att f&#229; sova tills solen gick upp.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:49,300" end="00:19:53,458">Jag s&#229;g med egna &#246;gon vad som h&#228;nde,<br/>eftersom alla p&#229; den tiden</p>
      <p begin="00:19:53,581" end="00:19:56,817">var h&#246;ga, de anv&#228;nde tunga droger.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:56,925" end="00:19:59,766">Men inte jag, jag h&#246;ll ett &#246;ga p&#229; dem<br/>medan de sk&#246;t upp</p>
      <p begin="00:19:59,766" end="00:20:01,183">och de f&#246;rs&#246;kte erbjuda mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:01,183" end="00:20:03,544">Men jag blev r&#228;dd, jag gillade inte n&#229;lar.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:03,544" end="00:20:05,021">Jag sa: "Nej, nej, nej."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:05,190" end="00:20:07,022">Det var d&#229; jag gick till Jobs Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:07,145" end="00:20:10,515">Jag f&#246;rs&#246;kte f&#229; mamma att <br/>registrera mig hos Jobs Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:10,622" end="00:20:12,854">Hon var arg p&#229; mig,<br/>s&#229; hon ville inte skriva p&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:12,977" end="00:20:15,088">S&#229; min syster f&#246;rfalskade<br/>hennes namnteckning.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:15,550" end="00:20:17,032">Jag l&#228;rde mig laga mat.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:17,140" end="00:20:19,089">Jag lagade mat i tv&#229; &#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:19,212" end="00:20:21,961">Jag var kockl&#228;rling i Bar Harbor, Maine.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:21,961" end="00:20:24,645">Det var d&#229; jag b&#246;rjade g&#246;ra James Brown,<br/>p&#229; Job Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:24,829" end="00:20:27,790">De sa, "Har ni sett den nya killen"?</p>
      <p begin="00:20:27,928" end="00:20:31,156">"Han ser precis ut som James Brown."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:32,231" end="00:20:36,840">Det gjorde mig peppad, de gav mig lite gin<br/>och det var s&#229; p&#229; det jobbet,</p>
      <p begin="00:20:36,840" end="00:20:39,036">man skulle smygdricka.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:39,736" end="00:20:42,175">De gav mig lite gin, jag blev full,</p>
      <p begin="00:20:42,299" end="00:20:44,505">de gav mig en mikrofon och sa: "Sjung."</p>
      <p begin="00:20:44,643" end="00:20:45,821">Och jag sl&#228;ppte loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:45,960" end="00:20:49,231">S&#229; de tog mig till <br/>ett Job Corpcenter f&#246;r tjejer</p>
      <p begin="00:20:49,231" end="00:20:51,358">f&#246;r att upptr&#228;da.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:51,358" end="00:20:53,110">Jag fr&#229;gade, "Hur stor &#228;r publiken?"</p>
      <p begin="00:20:53,217" end="00:20:54,678">De sa ungef&#228;r 20 eller 30.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:54,770" end="00:20:56,225">Jag sa "OK".</p>
      <p begin="00:20:56,548" end="00:20:59,096">De bad mig komma upp p&#229; scenen.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:59,403" end="00:21:01,168">Och jag tittade ut &#246;ver scenen.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:01,276" end="00:21:02,737">Jag s&#229;g alla m&#228;nniskor<br/>och jag kunde inte r&#246;ra mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:02,737" end="00:21:04,121">Jag sa:</p>
      <p begin="00:21:04,121" end="00:21:08,125">"Jag v&#228;grar g&#229; ut. Inte jag."</p>
      <p begin="00:21:08,125" end="00:21:13,205">S&#229; en kille som hette Moody<br/>gav mig en knuff.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:13,298" end="00:21:14,760">Jag s&#229;g att alla var glada.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:14,883" end="00:21:15,938">De &#228;lskade mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:16,030" end="00:21:17,898">De &#228;lskade att jag sj&#246;ng fr&#229;n hj&#228;rtat.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:18,329" end="00:21:22,091">Och jag t&#228;nkte:<br/>"Wow, det &#228;r h&#228;r jag h&#246;r hemma."</p>
      <p begin="00:21:22,214" end="00:21:23,843">Jag slutade aldrig efter det.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:26,981" end="00:21:29,903" region="top"> V&#229;r plan n&#228;r vi slutade i Job Corps,</p>
      <p begin="00:21:29,903" end="00:21:31,954" region="top"> var att tr&#228;ffas igen<br/>och forts&#228;tta med musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:31,954" end="00:21:35,205" region="top"> Mitt band blev skickade<br/>till Vietnamkriget.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:35,205" end="00:21:41,083" region="top"> De &#229;kte till kriget och jag gick klart<br/>min tr&#228;ning p&#229; Job Corps.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:47,414" end="00:21:49,499"/>
      <p begin="00:21:49,499" end="00:21:52,827"> </p>
      <p begin="00:21:52,827" end="00:21:56,698">- Jag vill smaka p&#229; den d&#228;r, <br/>n&#228;r du &#246;ppnade s&#229; var det en pumpa.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:56,698" end="00:21:58,097">- Ja, det &#228;r klart.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:58,097" end="00:21:59,297">- Jag m&#229;ste smaka p&#229; det d&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:21:59,297" end="00:22:00,821">- Vi kan &#246;ppna den nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:00,821" end="00:22:02,555">- Ett pumpa&#246;l, jag har aldrig <br/>h&#246;rt talas om pumpa&#246;l.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:02,555" end="00:22:03,541">- Ja, vi kan dricka lite av det.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:03,541" end="00:22:06,036">- Jag vill verkligen smaka.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:06,132" end="00:22:07,265">- OK.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:08,373" end="00:22:10,439">- Herregud, vad gott!</p>
      <p begin="00:22:10,439" end="00:22:12,132">- Pumpa&#246;l?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:12,132" end="00:22:13,572">- Seri&#246;st, det &#228;r helt otroligt.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:13,572" end="00:22:14,406">- &#196;r det pumpa?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:14,406" end="00:22:15,125">- Yo!</p>
      <p begin="00:22:15,125" end="00:22:16,318">- &#196;r det pumpan?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:16,318" end="00:22:20,223">- Det &#228;r s&#229; det p&#229;verkar vissa m&#228;nniskor.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:20,223" end="00:22:21,316">- Gillar du det nu?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:21,316" end="00:22:22,549">- Nej. - Gillar du det inte?</p>
      <p begin="00:22:22,549" end="00:22:23,575">- Jag gillar det helt enkelt inte.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:23,575" end="00:22:24,764">- Jag tycker det smakar uts&#246;kt.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:24,764" end="00:22:27,111">- Det &#228;r n&#229;gon typ av, pumpasmak d&#228;r i.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:27,296" end="00:22:29,471">- Att jobba med Charles Bradley<br/>&#228;r inte som att jobba med</p>
      <p begin="00:22:29,471" end="00:22:31,083">Sharon Lee eller n&#229;gon av de andra</p>
      <p begin="00:22:31,083" end="00:22:34,239">s&#229;ngarna fr&#229;n New York<br/>som jag ofta jobbar med</p>
      <p begin="00:22:34,239" end="00:22:37,143">Charles har dom galnaste historierna.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:37,339" end="00:22:38,983">De absolut galnaste.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:38,983" end="00:22:42,967">Jag sitter med honom och, <br/>l&#229;tskrivare som jag &#228;r</p>
      <p begin="00:22:43,075" end="00:22:45,738">h&#246;r jag hans historier och t&#228;nker att...</p>
      <p begin="00:22:45,845" end="00:22:48,796">Det d&#228;r m&#229;ste vi g&#246;ra en s&#229;ng av.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:48,796" end="00:22:51,394">S&#229; innan vi spelar in s&#229;ngen till en l&#229;t</p>
      <p begin="00:22:51,394" end="00:22:54,150">s&#228;tter jag p&#229; musiken och</p>
      <p begin="00:22:54,265" end="00:22:55,265">fr&#229;gar Charles om han gillar den.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:55,288" end="00:22:58,550">Sedan sjunger jag mina ide&#233;r f&#246;r honom,<br/>hur jag tycker att det ska vara.</p>
      <p begin="00:22:58,719" end="00:23:02,367">Inte f&#246;r att han avf&#228;rdar mina ide&#233;r,<br/>men han har sina egna</p>
      <p begin="00:23:02,367" end="00:23:05,407">och han b&#246;rjar uttrycka dem direkt.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:05,561" end="00:23:08,053">Han b&#246;rjar sjunga, och sen slutar vi</p>
      <p begin="00:23:08,161" end="00:23:09,930">och b&#246;rjar prata om n&#229;got annat en stund.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:09,930" end="00:23:11,289">- Pratar du med Charles</p>
      <p begin="00:23:11,289" end="00:23:15,336">tillr&#228;ckligt l&#228;nge kommer du att<br/>f&#229; h&#246;ra historier.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:15,336" end="00:23:18,842">Utan att jag fr&#229;gar, s&#229; b&#246;rjar han sjunga</p>
      <p begin="00:23:18,842" end="00:23:20,549">om vad vi pratade om.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:20,549" end="00:23:24,133">Sen h&#228;mtar jag en penna <br/>och l&#229;ter honom improvisera</p>
      <p begin="00:23:24,133" end="00:23:25,887">om och om igen.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:25,887" end="00:23:29,070">- Sen kollar vi igenom det igen<br/>och b&#246;rjar forma det till en s&#229;ng</p>
      <p begin="00:23:29,070" end="00:23:30,708">l&#229;ngsamt, under ett par timmar.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:30,815" end="00:23:34,330">Det &#228;r hans historier jag alltid<br/>f&#246;rs&#246;ker &#246;vers&#228;tta till en s&#229;ng.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:34,453" end="00:23:39,721"/>
      <p begin="00:23:39,875" end="00:23:45,113" region="top"> - Jag &#229;kte till Kalifornien 1977, <br/>jag s&#246;kte mina dr&#246;mmar, musiken.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:46,251" end="00:23:48,326">Jag hoppade mellan olika band.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:48,326" end="00:23:52,196">De sa: "Vi betalar dig 400 dollar<br/>f&#246;r att upptr&#228;da ikv&#228;ll".</p>
      <p begin="00:23:52,303" end="00:23:55,370">Han betalade mig f&#246;r att<br/>upptr&#228;da den kv&#228;llen.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:55,492" end="00:23:57,149">Det var s&#229; det funkade.</p>
      <p begin="00:23:57,488" end="00:24:01,896">Det var d&#229;, vet inte varf&#246;r,<br/>s&#229; blev jag v&#228;ldigt sjuk.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:02,035" end="00:24:06,613">Jag ringde min mamma<br/>och hon sa: "Kom hem."</p>
      <p begin="00:24:09,290" end="00:24:12,653">Mamma b&#246;rjade bli gammal<br/>och hon har varit med om mycket.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:12,745" end="00:24:16,686">Det &#228;r ju inte min uppgift att<br/>anklaga henne f&#246;r hur hon levt sitt liv.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:17,686" end="00:24:21,707" region="top"> S&#229; jag kom tillbaka till New York 1994.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:22,846" end="00:24:26,149" region="top"> Jag var riktigt sjuk, n&#228;ra att d&#246;.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:26,826" end="00:24:29,243" region="top"> De f&#246;rde mig till Woodhulls sjukhus.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:29,643" end="00:24:33,428" region="top"> Jag &#228;r allergisk mot penicillin<br/>och de gav mig penicillin</p>
      <p begin="00:24:33,705" end="00:24:36,235" region="top"> och min kropp st&#228;ngdes av.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:37,358" end="00:24:40,104" region="top"> Jag hade gett upp totalt.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:41,919" end="00:24:49,562">D&#229; kom min bror Joseph<br/>och bes&#246;kte mig p&#229; sjukhuset.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:50,070" end="00:24:52,881">Han b&#246;jde sig ner och pussade mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:24:52,881" end="00:24:54,978">Han sa "Nej, nej, Charles."</p>
      <p begin="00:24:55,163" end="00:24:56,783">Och han viskade i mitt &#246;ra</p>
      <p begin="00:24:56,968" end="00:25:02,406">Han sa "Min bror, om du inte vill leva <br/>f&#246;r dig sj&#228;lv, lev f&#246;r mig!"</p>
      <p begin="00:25:02,499" end="00:25:03,729">Han sa: "Charles, jag &#228;lskar dig."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:04,175" end="00:25:05,559">"Du &#228;r mitt hj&#228;rta."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:05,820" end="00:25:09,538">Jag sa: "Joe, jag ska k&#228;mpa.<br/>Jag ska k&#228;mpa."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:09,661" end="00:25:15,579"/>
      <p begin="00:25:15,579" end="00:25:19,675">Min bror sa till mig: <br/>"Charles, g&#246;r n&#229;got som du vill g&#246;ra."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:20,120" end="00:25:21,254">"F&#246;lj dina dr&#246;mmar."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:21,254" end="00:25:22,730">"Du &#228;lskar musik, g&#246;r musik."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:22,730" end="00:25:24,529">Och jag sa: "Jag vill vara smart som du."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:24,559" end="00:25:26,299">Han sa: "Nej brorsan, var inte som jag".</p>
      <p begin="00:25:26,422" end="00:25:27,839">"F&#246;rs&#246;k aldrig vara jag. Var dig sj&#228;lv."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:27,977" end="00:25:31,578" region="top"> - Det var hans kompis.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:32,055" end="00:25:34,077" region="top"> Joe gillade, var galen i Charles.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:34,200" end="00:25:37,948" region="top"> Han sa till Charles "Vad du &#228;n g&#246;r,<br/>g&#246;r det bra och forts&#228;tt k&#228;mpa."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:38,056" end="00:25:39,662" region="top"> "L&#229;t inte n&#229;gon prata dig ur det."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:39,969" end="00:25:42,668" region="top"> Det sa han innan han dog.</p>
      <p begin="00:25:42,713" end="00:25:46,356" region="top"> Han sa:<br/>"L&#229;t inte n&#229;gon prata dig ur det."</p>
      <p begin="00:25:46,402" end="00:26:02,360"/>
      <p begin="00:26:02,530" end="00:26:04,640">- Han sa: "Jag kan inte g&#246;ra det som du."</p>
      <p begin="00:26:04,716" end="00:26:06,824">Jag kommer ih&#229;g<br/>n&#228;r jag var liten, i Florida.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:07,009" end="00:26:10,779">Joseph gick p&#229; pianoskola<br/>och l&#228;rde sig alla sm&#229; detaljer,</p>
      <p begin="00:26:10,932" end="00:26:13,016">Jag l&#228;rde mig spela piano,<br/>genom att kolla p&#229; honom.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:13,724" end="00:26:16,478">Han visste aldrig detta - <br/>jag gjorde det sj&#228;lv.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:17,216" end="00:26:19,815">Han sa: "F&#246;lj dina dr&#246;mmar inom musiken"</p>
      <p begin="00:26:19,815" end="00:26:23,997">Han sa: "Ta ett av rummen <br/>och fixa till det"</p>
      <p begin="00:26:24,135" end="00:26:27,244">"G&#246;r det till ditt rum <br/>dit folk kan komma och repa."</p>
      <p begin="00:26:27,367" end="00:26:28,664">Det var det jag gjorde.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:29,171" end="00:26:31,328">Joey var b&#229;de som en pappa och en bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:31,421" end="00:26:33,748">Han var en underbar bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:33,867" end="00:26:39,326"/>
      <p begin="00:26:39,326" end="00:26:40,813">- Jaha, var &#228;r frukten?</p>
      <p begin="00:26:44,336" end="00:26:48,283"/>
      <p begin="00:26:48,283" end="00:26:49,966">- R&#228;cker det?</p>
      <p begin="00:26:49,966" end="00:26:51,130">- Lite mer.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:51,269" end="00:26:52,598">- Ja, s&#228;tt dig ner Charles, och &#228;t.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:52,598" end="00:26:54,603">- Jag g&#246;r bara lite frukost.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:54,603" end="00:26:55,804">- Jag &#228;r inte hungrig,<br/>det vet du. Men &#228;t du.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:55,942" end="00:26:59,512">Sen b&#246;rjar vi prata om vad du har gjort.</p>
      <p begin="00:26:59,620" end="00:27:00,716">- Okej, jag st&#228;ller den h&#228;r &#229;t dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:00,716" end="00:27:02,300">- Det g&#229;r bra.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:02,300" end="00:27:03,548">Jag l&#228;r upp Charles.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:03,671" end="00:27:07,320" region="top"> Jag skulle s&#228;ga att han &#228;r<br/>ungef&#228;r p&#229; dagis- eller f&#246;rstaklassniv&#229;</p>
      <p begin="00:27:07,458" end="00:27:09,933" region="top"> n&#228;r det g&#228;ller l&#228;sf&#246;rst&#229;else.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:10,179" end="00:27:15,653">- &#196;r de intresserade av min story?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:15,653" end="00:27:17,142">- Okej, du gjorde ljuden.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:17,142" end="00:27:19,132">F&#246;rstod du vad du l&#228;ste?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:21,228" end="00:27:24,710">- Hm, ja och nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:24,710" end="00:27:26,320">- Ja och nej.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:26,320" end="00:27:27,093">- Charles?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:27,093" end="00:27:28,407">- Hm?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:28,407" end="00:27:29,819" region="top"> - Lunchen var j&#228;ttegod.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:29,927" end="00:27:31,307">- Tack, mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:31,953" end="00:27:37,271">- Jag tror hans fr&#228;msta m&#229;l &#228;r att <br/>kunna skriva sina egna texter snabbt</p>
      <p begin="00:27:37,271" end="00:27:40,080">s&#229; fort de kommer in i hans huvud,</p>
      <p begin="00:27:40,080" end="00:27:43,296">f&#246;r han har m&#229;nga ord i huvudet<br/>som han vill skriva ner p&#229; papper.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:43,404" end="00:27:45,309">Men han vet inte hur man g&#246;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:45,355" end="00:27:46,372">- Du svarade inte "An" r&#228;tt. - OK</p>
      <p begin="00:27:46,372" end="00:27:48,381">- Jaha, tv&#229; N?</p>
      <p begin="00:27:48,381" end="00:27:49,498">- Bara ett N, inget D.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:49,498" end="00:27:51,239">- Jaha, N.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:51,239" end="00:27:53,705">- F&#246;r ordet OCH &#228;r n&#228;r du <br/>pratar om tv&#229; saker som du s&#228;tter ihop..</p>
      <p begin="00:27:53,705" end="00:27:55,332">- Okej, jag f&#246;rst&#229;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:55,332" end="00:27:56,661">- Fish AND chips.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:56,907" end="00:27:58,399">- OK. Jag kommer sakna dig.</p>
      <p begin="00:27:58,569" end="00:28:00,934">- Hejd&#229; Charles. Vi ses n&#228;sta vecka.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:01,103" end="00:28:02,172">Tack.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:02,203" end="00:28:30,261"/>
      <p begin="00:28:30,261" end="00:28:32,411">- Kom in.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:32,498" end="00:28:36,180">- Tar du det? Du kan l&#228;sa senare.<br/>Sluta med det d&#228;r nu.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:36,365" end="00:28:38,008">- Nej. Stick h&#228;r ifr&#229;n. - B&#246;rja jobba.</p>
      <p begin="00:28:39,547" end="00:28:41,505">- Du vet att jag &#228;ger dig.<br/>Du vet att jag &#228;r bossen.</p>
