      <p begin="00:46:33,230" end="00:46:34,488">ett par nya noter och s&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:46:34,488" end="00:46:36,488">Och jag sa: "Charles, <br/>h&#228;r &#228;r l&#229;ten till din bror."</p>
      <p begin="00:46:36,827" end="00:46:39,765">Han b&#246;rjade g&#246;ra sin grej, <br/>springa runt och skrika,</p>
      <p begin="00:46:39,842" end="00:46:42,420">"Det &#228;r s&#229; vackert, s&#229; vackert, <br/>herregud, herregud!"</p>
      <p begin="00:46:42,697" end="00:46:48,531">Sen b&#246;rjade vi jobba p&#229; den<br/>och det var sv&#229;rt, riktigt sv&#229;rt.</p>
      <p begin="00:46:48,685" end="00:46:56,936">Det var en v&#228;ldigt personlig och djup, <br/>m&#246;rk och hemsk historia om Charles bror.</p>
      <p begin="00:46:57,059" end="00:46:59,069">Dessutom en storebror, <br/>som han s&#229;g upp till och &#228;lskade.</p>
      <p begin="00:46:59,208" end="00:47:01,147">Han beh&#246;vde ber&#228;tta.</p>
      <p begin="00:47:01,301" end="00:47:25,261"/>
      <p begin="00:47:28,337" end="00:47:34,298">L&#229;net &#228;r jobbigt f&#246;r mig, <br/>jag tycker inte det &#228;r r&#228;ttvist.</p>
      <p begin="00:47:34,467" end="00:47:37,172">Har aldrig missat en betalning, <br/>f&#246;r de sa att om jag missar en betalning,</p>
      <p begin="00:47:37,295" end="00:47:39,660">kommer jag f&#229; 18% r&#228;nta.</p>
      <p begin="00:47:39,798" end="00:47:42,071">Jag har f&#246;rs&#246;kt ta nya l&#229;n, nya l&#229;n.</p>
      <p begin="00:47:42,210" end="00:47:44,098">De s&#228;ger att jag inte <br/>tj&#228;nar tillr&#228;ckligt med pengar.</p>
      <p begin="00:47:44,344" end="00:47:48,846">Jag sa: "Hur ska jag kunna <br/>tj&#228;na tillr&#228;ckligt med pengar</p>
      <p begin="00:47:48,939" end="00:47:51,318">n&#228;r jag betalar dessa dyra l&#229;n, <br/>jag ger mig ut</p>
      <p begin="00:47:51,487" end="00:47:55,521">och tj&#228;nar sm&#229;slantar, <br/>varje slant h&#229;ller mig flytande."</p>
      <p begin="00:47:56,090" end="00:47:57,943">- N&#228;r Joseph m&#246;rdades</p>
      <p begin="00:47:57,943" end="00:48:04,214">fick Charles ta &#246;ver allt ansvar <br/>f&#246;r vad hans mamma beh&#246;vde.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:04,214" end="00:48:06,442">Inte alla skulle ha gjort det.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:06,442" end="00:48:09,914">Charles har gett henne <br/>mycket av sina besparingar</p>
      <p begin="00:48:09,996" end="00:48:13,118">han investerar det i huset <br/>och hj&#228;lper henne att stanna d&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:13,426" end="00:48:19,502">- Han &#228;r p&#229; v&#228;g, skulle jag s&#228;ga, <br/>att k&#246;pa huset fr&#229;n sin mamma.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:20,425" end="00:48:25,461">Hans &#228;ldre syskon bor ocks&#229; i huset.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:25,800" end="00:48:27,510">Vill inte ha honom d&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:27,618" end="00:48:39,116">Han har ocks&#229; ett stort ansvar f&#246;r <br/>att ta hand om min systers aff&#228;rer.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:43,286" end="00:48:47,237"/>
      <p begin="00:48:48,303" end="00:48:49,552">- Hall&#229;.</p>
      <p begin="00:48:50,398" end="00:48:51,680">- Ja?</p>
      <p begin="00:48:53,357" end="00:48:55,131">- Hur m&#229;r du, Paul?</p>
      <p begin="00:48:56,546" end="00:49:01,861">Om hon inte kan l&#228;ra sig att renovera</p>
      <p begin="00:49:01,999" end="00:49:04,951">och l&#228;gga om l&#229;net p&#229; huset,<br/>d&#229; m&#229;ste hon v&#228;nta</p>
      <p begin="00:49:05,120" end="00:49:08,111">tills inkomstskatten kommer.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:08,434" end="00:49:11,670">N&#228;r den kommer, skulle hon vilja <br/>att jag sa upp min l&#228;genhet,</p>
      <p begin="00:49:11,670" end="00:49:13,463">men jag vill inte ge upp min l&#228;genhet.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:13,463" end="00:49:16,238">Om jag gjorde det s&#229; m&#229;ste jag <br/>flytta in i mammas hus.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:17,540" end="00:49:20,740">Som jag sa: "Min l&#228;genhet <br/>&#228;r det enda st&#228;llet jag har</p>
