      <p begin="00:49:22,571" end="00:49:27,281">och bara ta hand om mig sj&#228;lv."</p>
      <p begin="00:49:27,281" end="00:49:30,127">- Men vad du &#228;n g&#246;r, s&#229; vet jag att <br/>du g&#246;r det f&#246;r att hj&#228;lpa mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:30,220" end="00:49:31,246">och jag uppskattar det.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:31,246" end="00:49:32,115">Okej, Paul.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:32,115" end="00:49:32,991">Tack ska du ha, Paul.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:32,991" end="00:49:34,968">Okej.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:36,418" end="00:49:37,786">Vad har jag kvar att g&#246;ra?</p>
      <p begin="00:49:37,878" end="00:49:38,873">Det &#228;r mitt liv.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:38,873" end="00:49:40,384">Ta mitt liv ifr&#229;n mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:40,384" end="00:49:43,015">Ibland ber jag Gud att kalla hem mig.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:43,122" end="00:49:47,703">F&#246;r varje dag &#228;r jag ute och krigar <br/>f&#246;r att beh&#229;lla &#228;rligheten,</p>
      <p begin="00:49:47,857" end="00:49:51,311">anst&#228;ndigheten hos en m&#228;nniska <br/>som g&#229;r p&#229; denna planet</p>
      <p begin="00:49:51,434" end="00:49:55,135">att &#228;lska alla som Gud bett oss att g&#246;ra.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:55,858" end="00:49:59,353">Men idag ses det som en svaghet tror jag.</p>
      <p begin="00:49:59,923" end="00:50:05,079">Hur mycket mer kan en m&#228;nniska ge<br/>innan de hittar k&#228;rlek p&#229; planeten?</p>
      <p begin="00:50:05,202" end="00:50:07,281">Hur mycket mer kan man ge?</p>
      <p begin="00:50:07,574" end="00:50:12,191">Jag sa: "Fader, n&#228;r min stund &#228;r kommen."</p>
      <p begin="00:50:12,376" end="00:50:14,094">"&#196;r jag redo att g&#229;."</p>
      <p begin="00:50:14,707" end="00:50:17,243">Det &#228;r s&#229; jag k&#228;nner.</p>
