      <p begin="00:51:19,668" end="00:51:25,025">"&#196;r Sharon Jones lika stor i USA <br/>som hon &#228;r i Frankrike?"</p>
      <p begin="00:51:25,163" end="00:51:27,289">Och vi sa: "Nej nej."</p>
