      <p begin="00:51:40,040" end="00:51:43,705">S&#229; vi skrev en liten l&#229;t den kv&#228;llen:</p>
      <p begin="00:51:43,705" end="00:51:47,618">"Why Is It So Hard To Make It In America"</p>
      <p begin="00:51:47,772" end="00:51:52,676">Samma sekund som Charles sj&#246;ng <br/>"Why Is It So Hard To Make It In America"</p>
      <p begin="00:51:52,800" end="00:51:56,926">&#228;ndrades s&#229;ngens betydelse direkt.</p>
