      <p begin="00:51:59,193" end="00:52:11,071">&#9834; Varf&#246;r &#228;r det s&#229; sv&#229;rt<br/>att lyckas i USA? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:11,071" end="00:52:14,158">&#9834; Jag f&#246;rs&#246;ker &#9834;</p>
