      <p begin="00:52:29,798" end="00:52:33,969">&#9834; Varf&#246;r? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:33,969" end="00:52:36,430">&#9834; S&#228;g mig. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:36,430" end="00:52:43,562">&#9834; Vi m&#229;ste f&#246;r&#228;ndra USA. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:43,562" end="00:52:47,232">&#9834; Hj&#228;lp mig n&#229;gon &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:47,232" end="00:52:52,696">&#9834; Ohh... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:52:52,696" end="00:53:00,309"/>
      <p begin="00:53:00,309" end="00:53:01,247">- Kom hit.</p>
      <p begin="00:53:01,247" end="00:53:02,167">- Kom hit.</p>
      <p begin="00:53:02,167" end="00:53:03,843">Kom igen.</p>
