      <p begin="00:54:43,974" end="00:54:45,879">Jag ska definitivt skaffa den.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:46,448" end="00:54:48,146">Okej, Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:49,469" end="00:54:50,952">Sidan 6?</p>
      <p begin="00:54:51,382" end="00:54:52,700">Ja, okej, Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:54,638" end="00:54:55,850">Okej Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:56,527" end="00:54:58,386">Du ser, jag &#228;r skyldig dig s&#229; mycket.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:58,493" end="00:55:00,865">Ni &#228;r bara f&#246;r..Oh Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:00,865" end="00:55:02,690">Vi ses.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:02,690" end="00:55:04,212">Man har sina d&#229;liga sidor.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:05,580" end="00:55:06,891">Okej, Tommy.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:07,030" end="00:55:12,093">Tommy sa att jag fanns med <br/>i "The Post" p&#229; sidan 6.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:12,724" end="00:55:17,279">&#197;h Gud sig f&#246;rbarme.</p>
      <p begin="00:55:18,002" end="00:55:19,650">Vad s&#228;ger man?</p>
