      <p begin="00:55:35,965" end="00:55:37,791">Har du den, The Post?</p>
      <p begin="00:55:38,007" end="00:55:39,220">Har du The Post?</p>
      <p begin="00:55:40,250" end="00:55:43,648">Oj, han har inte The Post.</p>
