      <p begin="00:56:10,062" end="00:56:11,224">N&#228;men.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:13,916" end="00:56:15,637">Herregud.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:16,149" end="00:56:19,258"/>
      <p begin="00:56:19,258" end="00:56:23,665">Ja, herregud.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:23,788" end="00:56:25,137">Kolla p&#229; det h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:25,260" end="00:56:28,287">J&#228;klar, de fick med mig i tidningen.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:28,336" end="00:56:30,098">- Herre min skapare.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:30,098" end="00:56:31,816">- Vad g&#246;r du?</p>
      <p begin="00:56:31,923" end="00:56:33,903">- D&#228;r &#228;r jag.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:35,965" end="00:56:42,064">Jag tackar Gud f&#246;r detta, herregud.</p>
      <p begin="00:56:42,448" end="00:56:46,582">- Den h&#228;r killen har <br/>k&#228;mpat mycket med sig sj&#228;lv,</p>
