      <p begin="01:07:59,833" end="01:08:00,675">- Tre veckor?</p>
      <p begin="01:08:00,715" end="01:08:01,549">- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:01,549" end="01:08:02,912">- Jag kommer sakna dig min son.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:02,912" end="01:08:04,906">- Mm-hm. Du bor h&#228;r.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:05,029" end="01:08:06,174">Jag kommer ringa dig var tredje dag.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:06,174" end="01:08:08,630">- Okej &#228;lskling.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:13,310" end="01:08:15,430">- Jag &#228;r en bad boy.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:15,569" end="01:08:17,070">Du kan inte ta bort den h&#228;r k&#228;nslan.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:17,486" end="01:08:19,296">Du kan inte ta bort den h&#228;r k&#228;nslan.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:23,195" end="01:08:25,144">- Du kan inte retas. - Jag kan kittla dig.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:27,457" end="01:08:28,865">Jag kan kittla dig.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:28,865" end="01:08:39,527"/>
      <p begin="01:08:39,711" end="01:08:41,817">Som min mamma sa idag</p>
      <p begin="01:08:42,140" end="01:08:50,370">hon trodde aldrig att jag skulle <br/>ta mig till den h&#228;r niv&#229;n.</p>
      <p begin="01:08:50,450" end="01:09:01,860"/>
      <p begin="01:09:01,920" end="01:09:06,830">Jag vill se hur l&#229;ngt <br/>jag kan ta mig i livet.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:07,937" end="01:09:13,170">Se om jag kan ta mig l&#228;ngre <br/>&#228;n alla mina familjemedlemmar.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:13,585" end="01:09:16,133">Och du ser, det tog mig hit.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:17,441" end="01:09:19,466">Alla d&#228;r ute, se upp.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:19,589" end="01:09:22,876">En gammal man &#228;r p&#229; v&#228;g<br/>och jag g&#246;r ert jobb b&#228;ttre &#228;n ni.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:23,060" end="01:09:27,872">Om inte, g&#246;r jag det &#229;t er.</p>
      <p begin="01:09:31,686" end="01:10:03,522"/>
      <p begin="01:10:22,155" end="01:10:24,010">- Vill du jobba p&#229; den<br/>d&#228;r l&#229;ten fr&#229;n f&#246;rra veckan?</p>
      <p begin="01:10:24,148" end="01:10:25,229">- Vilken?</p>
      <p begin="01:10:25,367" end="01:10:26,862">- I Thank You (Jag tackar dig).</p>
      <p begin="01:10:26,986" end="01:10:52,255"/>
      <p begin="01:10:52,394" end="01:10:54,959">- Han b&#246;rjar verkligen bli bra.</p>
      <p begin="01:10:55,082" end="01:11:04,246"/>
      <p begin="01:11:04,246" end="01:11:07,062">Ahh!</p>
      <p begin="01:11:07,062" end="01:11:12,799">S&#229;dan &#228;r jag.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:12,799" end="01:11:21,486"/>
      <p begin="01:11:21,736" end="01:11:24,273">Woo.</p>
      <p begin="01:11:56,895" end="01:12:00,084">- N&#228;r jag l&#228;mnar den h&#228;r v&#228;rlden <br/>&#228;r v&#228;rlden inte skyldig mig n&#229;got.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:00,223" end="01:12:01,745">- Ge mig tillbaks min dollar nu.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:04,392" end="01:12:05,962">- L&#228;gg av.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:06,089" end="01:12:07,791">- Ge mig tillbaks min dollar.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:08,810" end="01:12:17,605"/>
      <p begin="01:12:17,605" end="01:12:18,666">- Mitt pass, v&#228;nta lite.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:18,804" end="01:12:39,516"/>
      <p begin="01:12:39,655" end="01:12:41,596">- Spara din hummer.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:43,227" end="01:12:46,111">- Jimmy, du &#228;ter inte hummer, <br/>du ger den alltid till mig.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:46,280" end="01:12:47,576">- Jag ska b&#246;rja &#228;ta det idag.</p>
      <p begin="01:12:47,791" end="01:13:09,549"/>
      <p begin="01:13:09,796" end="01:13:13,704">- Du &#228;r verkligen snabb, <br/>det &#228;r min quarter. Jag s&#229;g det.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:13,811" end="01:13:15,088">- Jag plockade upp den.</p>
      <p begin="01:13:15,268" end="01:14:18,880"/>
